Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:14.97,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1\pos(443.949,588.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:15.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:19.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:23.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:26.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:30.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:33.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:36.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:48.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:50.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:54.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:59.37,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:02.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:11.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:14.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:16.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:19.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What an awful night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So hot and humid...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Maybe we'll get some rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you've\Njust seen a ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A m-monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:19.33,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(480.495,236.833)}Tokageron and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:19.33,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(520.495,656.833)}the Monster Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The entrance is\Nblocked by a barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Created a barrier\Nwall, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.23,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H1D1EC0&}Authorized Personnel Only
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:54.24,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,A barrier—in other words, an invisible\Nwall made from electromagnetism.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:03:00.28,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Even a nuclear bomb\Ncannot breach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The Atomic Energy Research\NLaboratory is protected by a barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot attack the laboratory\Nuntil we destroy the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's too powerful\Nfor us to break through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of your whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's Japanese branch is lagging\Nbehind our European and American branches
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in forwarding our plans\Nfor world conquest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's another reason we need control of\Nthe Atomic Energy Research Laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That barrier is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It will bend, as all things do,\Nbefore the scientific might of Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My scientists...\Ngive them the barrier destruction ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the barrier destruction ball must be\Nthrown from a distance of twenty meters,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or it won't expel\Nthe necessary power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Additionally,\Nthe ball weighs five kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We possess no cyborg strong\Nenough to throw it twenty meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:04:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools! Make a cyborg strong\Nenough, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Professional soccer\Nplayer Ken Nomoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:33.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's one of the best center\Nforward players in the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:36.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His killer goal shot is\Nfeared by players everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Nomoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost. Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no time for kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sign my book!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you lazy fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be in dead last place\Nif you didn't have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a toast,\Nto the health of the great Ken Nomoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bunch of layabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken Nomoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's computer\Ngave us your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me, Ken Nomoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you the most\Npowerful man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't take orders from anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You will join us,\Nas one of Shocker's cyborgs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you be leaving your wife\Nalone this soon after the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got homemaker\Ntraining to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to start early.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And men have their\Nown work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You cad. Listen to you talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real mind reader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wasted on this café.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't raise him up too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro's a simple man,\Nsusceptible to flattery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always like this, Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Work matters aside,\NI have a question to ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's where you'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.34,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H00000&}Two Security Guards Killed\NToyo Atomic Energy Research Laboratory\NCould an International Spy Organization be Behind It?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.93,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,It must be Shocker\Nwho attacked the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.72,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Atomic Energy Research Laboratory\Nand killed those security guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:34.64,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,They'll be mounting a new\Nattack sooner than later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.69,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I'll keep it safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:39.44,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,If that laboratory is destroyed\Nand the radiation leaks out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:41.65,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,it'll destroy all of\NTokyo in ten minutes flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken Nomoto's transplant\Nsurgery is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Honored scientists of Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,show me the fusion of\Nhuman and venomous lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of a venomous\Nlizard to kill an elephant,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,combined with the kicking\Npower of soccer star Ken Nomoto
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,has created the lizard\Nman, Tokageron,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,designed to kick the\Nbarrier destruction ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Send our spies to the\Nresearch facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Find the barrier's weakest\Npoint, then attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We will turn Japan's capital,\NTokyo, into a wasteland!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That Hongo is such\Na slavedriver...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Making me stand watch\Nin a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he even go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That car just passed\Nby a few minutes ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the third pass they've\Ndone of the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be\NShocker's secret base.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...\NI'll find out what's going on inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be the era of\Nwomen's lib and feminism,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but you must agree that\Nthis is a man's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo will chew me\Nout if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please.\NThey're made out of clay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of freak would\Ncollect these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the master of this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you break\Ninto my property?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see...\NI'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The only ones in\Nthis house besides me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,are these statues.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the one who\Ncollects these weird things?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I must ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a lousy sense of\Ntaste, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot leave that man alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I will finish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider\Ndefeated all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you're losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get an opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave everything to\Nthe great Tokageron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:06.14,Bumper Episode 2-13,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(355,530)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki... are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko... I'm fine, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to safety! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the Kamen Rider\NI've heard so much about...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:14:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for\Nyou to show yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Shocker's new\Ncyborg, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold Tokageron's kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Rider will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is\Nno match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider has lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to believe it,\Nbut I saw it with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a week's\Npeace and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider lost\Nto that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to find\Nout our next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:19.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At that moment, Hongo Takeshi—rather,\NKamen Rider—was in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:21.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was desperate to\Nperfect a new move that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,would get him past\NTokageron's deadly kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't endure a few rocks,\Nthere's no way I can beat his kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago,\NI trained you on this mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to make you the\Nworld's greatest racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It nearly drove you mad,\Nbut you endured everything I threw at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo. Will you put\Nyourself through that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana... I will learn to\Ncounter that killer kick of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I must learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just let it hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Use more of your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I double the power I\Nput into the Rider Kick...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana,\Nthrow the rock from where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Kamen Rider is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Taki's ID?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki Kazuya...\NFBI special agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. He's in the FBI...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he was so desperate to poke\Nhis nose into the investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...\Nhe's after Shocker right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,With Rider out of the fight, I'll put\Nmy life on the line to destroy Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my mission,\Nas an FBI agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, FBI scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The eleven Shocker\Ncyborgs you saw before
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,are already on their way to the\NAtomic Energy Research Laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But you will not\Nleave here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get to\Nthe laboratory...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to unleash\Nits radiation on Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take any barrier\Ndown in one hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all the cyborgs\NI killed before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocked, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But cyborgs cannot die...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we repair\Nthe parts you destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't even\Nbeat me on your own...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you expect to\Nfight eleven of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can die with my\Ndestruction ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for my killer shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lighting Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rider Kick beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.97,0:22:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I defeated all eleven monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're incredible, Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.20,0:23:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's willing to give his life\Nto protect people, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't bring peace and\Nhappiness to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,if you only ever\Nthink about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:27.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi once again saved\NTokyo from Shocker's evil plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:31.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker would surely attack again\Nin their quest to take over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:35.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider would\Ncontinue to fight with
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:37.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,no end, for the sake\Nof peace and justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:40.66,Cont,,560,0,140,,{\blur.8\fad(0,430)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:43.32,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(502.031,486.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:45.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next week will be the start\Nof a new Kamen Rider series.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:49.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With a new costume and\Nlots of new things to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.49,0:23:51.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,you'll find thrills and action.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:24:00.74,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,210.389)}The Devilish Sabotegron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:24:00.74,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(367.167,520.389)}Attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:58.04,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for Kamen Rider:\N"The Devilish Sabotegron Attacks!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:10.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.39,0:24:13.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.39,0:24:15.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:18.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.90,0:24:20.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.77,0:24:22.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:24.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.44,0:24:25.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.24,0:24:28.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.32,0:24:33.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.99,0:24:37.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.58,0:24:41.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.67,0:24:45.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!